g.text: After selecting under which major each holder serves, 1 holder from each community will be voted to represent them. The person voted will be lended the Eli major for 3 month and will be leading his troops and shaping the community alongside the team, each 3 month a new leader will be elected.
Elis get access to special token gated tools to interact with and shape the story, which is then turned into animated episodes and comic material for the brand, while accumulating reward points.
Holders can redeem their reward points inside our marketplace, where we'll have different rewards catered to the community's interests.
New tools and minigames will be built in which the outcome will decide the fate of how the story plays out.

Eli's brand will look to expand both inside and outside of web3, reaching out to the masses and helping bring global attention to the brand through partner marketing and having an offline and online presence.
The holders will be able to hop into their 3D Elis and play the story that they have been building in an immersive 3D world we will be building.
Eli holders will get the chance to upgrade their Elis into a 3D character which they can then use in upcoming experiences or inside a metaverse.
